    </div>

    <div id="loading" style="text-align: center;">ƒêang t·∫£i b·ªô th·∫ª...</div>
    <div id="finished" style="display:none; text-align: center;">
        <i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="font-size: 4rem; color: #10b981; margin-bottom: 20px;"></i>
        <h3>Ho√†n th√†nh xu·∫•t s·∫Øc!</h3>
        <p>B·∫°n ƒë√£ √¥n h·∫øt th·∫ª b√†i h√¥m nay.</p>
        <a href="/my-tree" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 10px;">V·ªÅ V∆∞·ªùn D√πng Ph√¢n B√≥n üå±</a>
    </div>

    <div id="reviewArea" style="display:none;">
        <div class="flashcard-scene" onclick="flipCard()">
            <div class="flashcard" id="currentCard">
                <div class="card-face front">
                    <small style="color:#999; margin-bottom: 10px;">C√¢u h·ªèi</small>
                    <div class="card-content" id="txtFront">?</div>
                    <div style="margin-top: 20px; color: #cbd5e1; font-size: 0.9rem;">(Ch·∫°m ƒë·ªÉ l·∫≠t)</div>
